        "richtext_VWaj6X": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Travel rings are designed to give you the freedom to enjoy life’s moments without worry. Whether you’re heading abroad, spending time at the beach or simply living day to day, a travel ring allows you to wear something beautiful while keeping your most valuable pieces safe.</p><p>A travel ring is typically worn in place of your engagement ring or promise ring, offering the same elegant look without the risk. Many people choose travel rings to protect sentimental jewellery from loss, damage or theft, especially when travelling or in busy environments.</p><p>At The Promise Co, our travel rings are designed to do more than just replace your original ring. They are created to feel meaningful in their own right, combining elegant design with everyday practicality so you never have to compromise on style or sentiment.</p>"
          }
        }
