        "richtext_x6mKez": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A travel ring gives you confidence to wear a ring without the worry that often comes with more valuable jewellery. It allows you to enjoy your experiences fully, knowing your original piece is safe.</p><ul><li>Protects sentimental rings from loss, damage or theft</li><li>Designed for travel, holidays and everyday wear</li><li>Offers the same elegant look without the risk</li><li>A practical alternative for active lifestyles</li></ul><p>Many people choose travel rings not only for holidays, but also for work, exercise or daily routines where wearing a high-value ring may not be practical.</p><p>A practical ring without losing meaning</p><p>While travel rings are often seen as a practical solution, they can still carry<br/>meaning. Rather than replacing your original ring entirely, they act as an extension of it, allowing you to keep the symbolism while adapting to different moments in your life.</p>"
          }
        }
