            "question": "What is a travel ring?",
            "answer": "<p>A travel ring is a ring worn in place of your engagement ring, wedding ring or promise ring when travelling or in situations where wearing valuable jewellery may not be practical. It is designed to offer a similar look while reducing the risk of loss or damage.</p>"
