          "settings": {
            "question": "Why do people wear travel rings?",
            "answer": "<p>People wear travel rings to protect valuable or sentimental jewellery. They are especially useful for holidays, busy environments or active situations where there is a higher risk of losing or damaging a ring.</p>"
