        "question_4wRLV3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are travel rings only for holidays?",
            "answer": "<p>No. While travel rings are popular for holidays, they are also worn for everyday activities such as going to the gym, commuting or working with your hands. They offer a practical alternative whenever wearing expensive jewellery feels risky.</p>"
